title: Superstar College Girls Makeover
description: Superstar College Girls Makeover is a trendy dress-up game where you style a squad of five fashionistas with the latest superstar clothing collections. Give high school BFFs a total fashion makeover by adjusting facial features, skin tones, hair, and makeup. Dress each star girl uniquely for parties, performances, or school, with a vast wardrobe, makeup, accessories, and hairstyles. Elevate your stylist skills in this ultimate college girls' makeover experience!
